reviewText:
THIS IS A TOTALLY AWESOME VHS!!!!GREAT SOUND PICTURE QUALITY!!!JUST  CAN NOT SAY ENOUGH!!!!!THANKS VERY MUCH!!!HIGHLY RECOMMENDED A+++++

SUPER FAST SHIPPING!!!

This is the second part of a 2 volume movie set highlighting the Moscow Music Peace Festival from August 12th and 13th, 1989.  It has concert footage from Motley Crue, Gorky Park, Ozzy Osbourne, Scorpions and an awesome jam which went on at the end of the concert.  It also has alot of backstage footage with the bands and fans.  This is one movie you must have!
